title: ProtocolObjectTypesSupported (Property)
text:
PROPERTY ProtocolObjectTypesSupported : STRING
Supported object types. The meaning of each bit in this Bit-String can be found in the BACnet standard.
The preconfigured value of 111111111110111111111001110101 corresponds to the object types provided
by this BACnet Stack/API/Library and which have an FB representation in this API. At least 18 bits are needed.
